msgid "Drag-and-drop AppImage installer and management application"
msgstr "Suiteálaí agus feidhmchlár bainistíochta AppImage tarraing-agus-titim"

#: data/com.github.AppManager.metainfo.xml:35
msgid ""
"AppManager lets you install or uninstall AppImages with a familiar drag-and-"
"drop workflow inspired by macOS. It handles desktop integration, icon "
"extraction, executable bits, and app updates."
msgstr ""
"Le AppManager is féidir leat AppImages a shuiteáil nó a dhíshuiteáil le "
"sreabhadh oibre tarraing-agus-titim atá coitianta agus atá spreagtha ag "
"macOS. Láimhseálann sé comhtháthú deisce, eastóscadh deilbhíní, giotáin "
"inrite, agus nuashonruithe aipeanna."
